text: KJRM-LP (93.3 FM, "Sonshine 93.3") is a low-power FM radio station licensed to McAlester, Oklahoma, United States. The station is currently owned by JR Ministries Educational Association. ==References== ==External links== * JRM-LP JRM-LP Category:Contemporary Christian radio stations in the United States Category:Pittsburg County, Oklahoma Category:Radio stations established in 1975
